OL,7,FThe council executive will vote on
OL,8,Fwhether to allocate the funding for
OL,9,Fthe project at their meeting next week
OL,10,Fon March 27.
OL,12,FThe road will not be completely
OL,13,Frestored, as per the recommendations
OL,14,Fof a recent review into the scheme by
OL,15,Fconsultants.
OL,17,FHowever, much of the sea-facing
OL,18,Fparking will be restored, the wavy
OL,19,Flines and two-way cycle path will be
OL,20,Fremoved, and the roundabout will
OL,21,Fbecome a standard mini-roundabout.
