OL,8,Fand there will be a single contraflow
OL,9,Fcycle lane.
OL,11,FHannah Young, the council's executive
OL,12,Fmember for highways and transport,
OL,13,Fsaid: "These changes support the
OL,14,Ffindings of the independent review
OL,15,Fwhich was commissioned following
OL,16,Fconcerns from residents and businesses
OL,17,Fin the town.
