OL,7,F"Clevedon seafront has been a key
OL,8,Fpriority for the Clevedon community.
OL,9,FThe changes proposed are a priority
OL,10,Fbecause they focus on safety or
OL,11,Faddressing disability access issues.
OL,13,F"If they are agreed by the Council's
OL,14,FExecutive next week, I'm committed to
OL,15,Fcontinue to engage with local people
OL,16,Fto finalise the plans and plan
OL,17,Fimplementation."
OL,19,FThe executive will meet at 2.30pm on
OL,20,FMarch 27 in Weston-super-Mare Town
OL,21,FHall.
